metadata.name: Unshackled
metadata.description: Unshackled is a powerful and inspiring piece of art that speaks to the human experience of feeling constrained or limited by social expectations, past experiences, or other external forces. Finding freedom from these shackles and being able to be true to oneself can be a challenging journey, but it can also be a rewarding and liberating experience. It's great to see art that encourages self-discovery and encourages people to embrace their own unique paths.
